column5: Just curious if any of you are members of this local club? I am not able to find much info on the club. Thanks
One of my best friends is a member. I can give you his phone number if you want.
i'm a member what ya want to know? they have-100yd 50yd and 25 yd rifle range -hand gun range - archery range -3d course - trap 2 ranges -fishing pond full of bows and specks - camping sites
im not sure of the exact prices but i do know that it costs me around 280.00 a year . this includes -family membership to the club -ofah family membership -rights to all ranges
Welcome to the board! PM sent! Thanks
